Novus Zone 🌐
Welcome to the official repository for Novus Zone — a modern, responsive website built to explore, create, and connect.

🚀 About
Novus Zone is a dynamic online platform designed to provide users with an interactive and engaging experience. The website is built with performance, accessibility, and scalability in mind.

🛠️ Tech Stack
Frontend: HTML, CSS, JavaScript 

Backend: TBD

Styling: Tailwind CSS 

Hosting: GitHub Pages

🌟 Features
Fully responsive design

Smooth UI interactions

Fast load times and optimized performance
